{"tid":689104,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"地盤的決擇","createTime":"2018-06-03T23:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T01:20:50.000Z","uid":8914,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0360681455fbf8bdff0891c2cab0e9d975a382","tid":689104,"uid":8914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T23:15:02.000Z","msg":"我今年 年頭先轉行做地盤，<br />\n<br />\n跟我朋友個老豆做燈喉， 850$日<br />\n<br />\n本身請我反去會叫我上樓面，但因為太多師傅既關係，<br />\n<br />\n叫我係下邊開料，執頭執尾咁啦，<br />\n<br />\n咁現家都做左都接近半年，樓面都起貨，個大佬就同個老闆就接埋樓籠既磚間，穿線做，而我就依然做埋d無謂野，e.g 清箱，T水線，執喉咁🤦🏻&zwj;♂️🤦🏻&zwj;♂️ 同做雜工無分別，有時真係做到好灰，覺得自己好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到左早兩日有位師傅拉我走，又係做燈喉，950$日<br />\n<br />\n會幫手上樓面做同要幫手開鐵喉料，但問題就係，諗緊會唔會又係水我去正係開鐵喉料，無得學樓面既野🤦🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n現家1516跟唔跟好，我本身個大佬就唔怕無工開既，只係做既野同做老雜無分別，而拉我走果個師傅，佢地就係固定班底一齊做開的"},{"pid":"5f4d7102e8893c176bc54978f9a0687c6a457ff9","tid":689104,"uid":172840,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T23:17:21.000Z","msg":"多一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6a99266ee7e45cabf2779fadac0049d4e92e9e","tid":689104,"uid":68098,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T23:17:37.000Z","msg":"年紀唔大既就跟人轉啦<br />\n跳去第二邊又識多D 人"},{"pid":"48f6df1d6b71cca4235775a97959424e4c3371e8","tid":689104,"uid":8914,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T23:22:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年紀唔大既就跟人轉啦<br />\n跳去第二邊又識多D 人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年26，有家室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc030fc155e9403a7193644a236f38878a033e24","tid":689104,"uid":118502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f4d7102e8893c176bc54978f9a0687c6a457ff9","tid":689104,"uid":172840,"like":1,"dislike":5